Two ffmpeg-core.wasm builds are included, both LGPL-2.1:

  - Audio-only (~1.5 MB) — custom build with AC3/EAC3/DTS decoders and
    AAC encoder. Loaded when only audio transcode is needed.
  - Full (~32 MB) — stock @ffmpeg/core 0.12.10 build with all native
    ffmpeg codecs. Loaded on demand as a fallback.

Both binaries are loaded at runtime as separate .wasm files and are not
compiled into the JavaScript bundle. Users may substitute them with
modified versions, satisfying LGPL's relinkability requirement.

Neither build includes GPL-licensed external libraries (x264, x265,
libfdk-aac). Only native ffmpeg codecs (all LGPL) are compiled in.
